text: Star Bharat () is a Hindi language Indian television channel. It is a part of Star India which is fully owned by 21st Century Fox. ==Current TV programs == ===Currently broadcast=== ====Comedy series==== * Kya Haal, Mr. Paanchal *Excuse Me Maadam ====Drama series==== * Jiji Maa' *Mayavi Maaling *Muskaan * Nimki Mukhiya * Saam Daam Dand Bhed * Savdhaan India *ChandraShekhar (TV Series) ===Formerly broadcast=== ====Drama series==== * Ayushman Bhava * Kaal Bhairav Rahasya ===Comedy series=== *Jai Kanhaiya Lal Ki ====Reality/non- scripted programming==== *Golden Divas Baatein With the Baadshah * Om Shanti Om ==References== Category:Television channels in India category:2017 establishments in Asia
